MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 1 : Increases maximum shield based on Constructor Site Rating. Each level thereafter increases power flow to B.A.S.E. structures, increasing it's visibility.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 1 : Increases maximum shield based on Constructor Site Rating. Each level thereafter increases power flow to B.A.S.E. structures, increasing it's visibility.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 2 : Lofty Architecture : Increase the health of B.A.S.E. connected structures by 20%.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 2 : Lofty Architecture : Increase the health of B.A.S.E. connected structures by 20%.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 3 : Increases energy regeneration based on Constructor Site Rating.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 3 : Increases energy regeneration based on Constructor Site Rating.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 4 : Safety Protocols: Increase the damage resistance of B.A.S.E. connected structures by 15%
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 4 : Safety Protocols: Increase the damage resistance of B.A.S.E. connected structures by 15%

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 5 : Neuro Stimulus Loop : Allies within the area of B.A.S.E. regenerate 1% of total Energy per second while inside the area of B.A.S.E.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 5 : Neuro Stimulus Loop : Allies within the area of B.A.S.E. regenerate 1% of total Energy per second while inside the area of B.A.S.E.
